# Free Deploy MD1 - Neon + Render + Vercel

Ovo je detaljno uputstvo za ovaj projekat:

- Database: Neon PostgreSQL
- Backend/API: Render Web Service
- Frontend: Vercel
- Lokalni projekat: `C:\programming\hidzamaaaa`

## 0. Važna greška koju si dobio na Renderu

Na Renderu si dobio:

```text
TS7016: Could not find a declaration file for module 'bcryptjs'
TS7016: Could not find a declaration file for module 'nodemailer'
TS7016: Could not find a declaration file for module 'jsonwebtoken'
```

Uzrok: Render kod tebe nije imao TypeScript `@types` pakete tokom builda.

Popravka je već urađena u projektu:

- `backend/package.json` sada ima TypeScript, Prisma, TSX i `@types/*` u `dependencies`
- `backend/src/routes/public.ts` ima eksplicitne tipove za dva callbacka
- lokalni `npm run build` u backendu prolazi

Prije novog deploya moraš pushati ove izmjene na GitHub.

```bash
git add .
git commit -m "Fix Render backend build and add deploy guide"
git push
```

Ako nisi još napravio Git repo:

```bash
git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial deploy"
git branch -M main
git remote add origin https://github.com/USERNAME/hidzama.git
git push -u origin main
```

## 1. Neon PostgreSQL

### 1.1 Napravi Neon projekat

1. Otvori https://neon.tech
2. New Project
3. Izaberi region blizu Evrope ako može
4. Sačuvaj connection string

### 1.2 Koji connection string uzeti

Za ovaj Render backend najjednostavnije uzmi Neon direct PostgreSQL connection string, ne pooled, zato što backend na startu pokreće Prisma migracije.

Treba izgledati otprilike ovako:

```env
postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@HOST.neon.tech/DBNAME?sslmode=require
```

Ako Neon da URL bez `sslmode=require`, dodaj na kraj:

```text
?sslmode=require
```

Ako URL već ima `?`, onda dodaj:

```text
&sslmode=require
```

Primjer:

```env
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://sifa_owner:password@ep-example.eu-central-1.aws.neon.tech/sifa?sslmode=require
```

Nemoj stavljati navodnike oko `DATABASE_URL` u Render dashboardu.

## 2. Render backend

Backend ide na Render kao Web Service.

### 2.1 Napravi Web Service

1. Otvori https://render.com
2. New
3. Web Service
4. Connect GitHub repo
5. Izaberi repo `hidzama`
6. Runtime: Node
7. Instance: Free

### 2.2 Render postavke

Postavi tačno ovako:

```text
Name: hidzama-api
Root Directory: backend
Runtime: Node
Branch: main
Build Command: npm install && npm run db:generate && npm run build
Start Command: npm run db:migrate && npm run db:seed && npm start
```

Ako opet vidiš grešku za `@types`, koristi ovu build komandu:

```text
npm install --include=dev && npm run db:generate && npm run build
```

Ali nakon zadnje popravke ne bi trebalo.

### 2.3 Render environment variables

U Renderu idi na:

```text
Service -> Environment -> Add Environment Variable
```

Dodaj:

```env
NODE_ENV=production
PORT=4000
DATABASE_URL=OVDJE_IDE_NEON_DATABASE_URL
JWT_SECRET=napravi_dug_random_secret_minimum_32_znaka_123
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=7d
ADMIN_EMAIL=admin@sifahidzama.ba
ADMIN_PASSWORD=PromijeniOvoOdmah123!
FRONTEND_URL=https://tvoj-vercel-url.vercel.app
BACKEND_URL=https://hidzama-api.onrender.com
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_SECURE=false
SMTP_USER=tvojgmail@gmail.com
SMTP_PASS=tvoj_google_app_password
MAIL_FROM=Sifa Hidžama <tvojgmail@gmail.com>
NOTIFY_EMAIL=tvojgmail@gmail.com
```

Za tvoju trenutnu Render adresu sa screenshota vjerovatno:

```env
BACKEND_URL=https://hidzama.onrender.com
```

Kasnije kad Vercel napravi frontend URL, vrati se u Render i promijeni:

```env
FRONTEND_URL=https://tvoj-vercel-url.vercel.app
```

Nakon promjene environment variables klikni:

```text
Manual Deploy -> Clear build cache & deploy
```

### 2.4 Provjeri backend

Kad deploy prođe, otvori:

```text
https://hidzama.onrender.com/health
```

Treba vratiti nešto kao:

```json
{"ok":true,"service":"sifa-hijama-api"}
```

API baza:

```text
https://hidzama.onrender.com/api/services
```

Treba vratiti JSON listu usluga.

## 3. Vercel frontend

Frontend ide na Vercel.

### 3.1 Napravi Vercel projekat

1. Otvori https://vercel.com
2. Add New Project
3. Import GitHub repo
4. Framework Preset: Vite
5. Root Directory: `frontend`

### 3.2 Vercel build postavke

Postavi:

```text
Framework Preset: Vite
Root Directory: frontend
Build Command: npm run build
Output Directory: dist
Install Command: npm install
```

### 3.3 Vercel environment variable

Dodaj environment variable:

```env
VITE_API_URL=https://hidzama.onrender.com/api
```

Važno: mora početi sa `VITE_`, jer Vite/Vercel samo tako izloži varijablu frontend kodu.

Ako Render backend URL nije `https://hidzama.onrender.com`, koristi svoj tačan Render URL.

Primjer:

```env
VITE_API_URL=https://hidzama-api.onrender.com/api
```

Nakon dodavanja env varijable uradi redeploy na Vercelu.

## 4. Poveži Render i Vercel

Kad Vercel deploy završi, dobit ćeš URL npr:

```text
https://hidzama.vercel.app
```

Vrati se na Render backend environment variables i postavi:

```env
FRONTEND_URL=https://hidzama.vercel.app
```

Zatim u Renderu klikni:

```text
Manual Deploy -> Deploy latest commit
```

Ovo je važno zbog CORS zaštite. Backend dozvoljava requeste samo sa `FRONTEND_URL`.

## 5. Admin login

Kad je sve deployano, otvori:

```text
https://hidzama.vercel.app/admin/login
```

Login:

```text
Email: vrijednost iz ADMIN_EMAIL
Password: vrijednost iz ADMIN_PASSWORD
```

Primjer:

```text
Email: admin@sifahidzama.ba
Password: PromijeniOvoOdmah123!
```

## 6. Email notifikacije

Za Gmail moraš koristiti Google App Password, ne normalnu Gmail lozinku.

### Koraci

1. Uključi 2-Step Verification na Google account
2. Otvori Google App Passwords
3. Napravi app password za Mail
4. Kopiraj 16-character password
5. U Render stavi:

```env
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_SECURE=false
SMTP_USER=tvojgmail@gmail.com
SMTP_PASS=abcdefghijklmnop
MAIL_FROM=Sifa Hidžama <tvojgmail@gmail.com>
NOTIFY_EMAIL=amir@gmail.com
```

`NOTIFY_EMAIL` je email gdje vlasnik prima obavijest za rezervaciju i kontakt formu.

Ako hoćeš da Amir prima na Gmail:

```env
NOTIFY_EMAIL=amirov.email@gmail.com
```

## 7. Najčešći problemi

### Problem: Render build failed sa TS7016

Rješenje:

1. Uradi `git pull`/provjeri da imaš zadnje izmjene
2. Pushaj `backend/package.json` i `backend/package-lock.json`
3. Render -> Manual Deploy -> Clear build cache & deploy

Alternativna build komanda:

```text
npm install --include=dev && npm run db:generate && npm run build
```

### Problem: Vercel sajt se otvori, ali podaci ne rade

Provjeri `VITE_API_URL`.

Mora biti:

```env
VITE_API_URL=https://tvoj-render-backend.onrender.com/api
```

Ne smije biti:

```env
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:4000/api
```

### Problem: CORS error u browseru

U Render backendu `FRONTEND_URL` mora biti tačan Vercel URL:

```env
FRONTEND_URL=https://tvoj-vercel-url.vercel.app
```

Nakon toga redeploy backend.

### Problem: Prisma migrate ne radi sa Neon

Provjeri da `DATABASE_URL` ima:

```text
sslmode=require
```

Koristi direct Neon connection string za migracije. Ako koristiš pooled URL i migracije prave problem, prebaci na direct URL.

### Problem: admin user nije kreiran

Render start command mora sadržavati:

```text
npm run db:migrate && npm run db:seed && npm start
```

Seed kreira admin korisnika iz:

```env
ADMIN_EMAIL
ADMIN_PASSWORD
```

### Problem: Render free je spor

To je normalno. Render free instance spava kad nema aktivnosti. Prvi request može čekati 50+ sekundi.

