## 9. Redoslijed deploya

Najlakši redoslijed:

1. Neon baza
2. Render backend
3. Provjeri `https://render-url/health`
4. Provjeri `https://render-url/api/services`
5. Vercel frontend
6. U Render `FRONTEND_URL` postavi na Vercel URL
7. Redeploy Render
8. Test login
9. Test booking
10. Test email
